  title: Broccoli Tree Factory Scene
  description: This scene contains a Broccoli Tree Factory with a pipeline to produce
    trees.\n\nSelect the 'Broccoli Tree Factory' GameObject on the Hierarchy Panel,
    then click on the 'Open Tree Editor Window' button on the Inspector Panel.\n\nThe
    Tree Editor Panel contains the Pipeline to produce trees, selecting a node lets
    you customize aspects from the tree.\n\nOn the Tree Editor Panel click on the
    'Generate New Preview' button to randomize the tree creation process. You can
    also load a new pipeline by clicking on the 'From Catalog' button.\n\nHappy Tree
    Designing!
